{
  "stem": "17001.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then we didn't know when is our turn that we will be leaving the house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we had slept with two and three dresses on, figuring that this way, we don't know how much they let us take, so that we will have the dresses on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in April, from 15 until the 17th when they took us away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1944.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we slept with our clothing on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I mentioned, my brother wasn't allowed to travel, so he came back and he had a knapsack, because we had bought a knapsack for him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father had a knapsack, because he was called into the working battalion, so at that time he was outfitted with a raincoat, with a knapsack.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Meantime, we had given some of the suits from my father and my brother and some of the better clothing and beddings and all this better things to our neighbor who wasn't Jewish, but her husband was a Jewish lawyer who was called into the working battalion and he was there and they had a little girl.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we knocked on the window and she took it in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said-- I gave it to her and I said that we don't know what will be our future, but then we come back, then you will please give it back to us, because we will pay you for it, holding it.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She said, oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Give me whatever you want.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I will keep it for you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, we even had a big basket full of eggs from-- from Passover that was left over.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I hand it to her also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What happened is that finally it was our turn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They came to us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when a-- two gendarme comes.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
